{
  "stem": "19807.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had our own-- our own Jewish community center.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They confiscated that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Maccabi salon, the Maccabi gym, which was a beautiful gym, brand new, and it was right in the area of-- of the school, was confiscated by the Fascists.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were not able to pray the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] luckily, that was the first year.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, interesting thing, though, they allow us to go to Bulgarian schools, not to Hebrew schools.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was able to go to a Bulgarian school and to go to high school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was the only Bulgarian-- I was the only Jew amongst 55 Bulgarians.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know, but it was something with me as a kid, I always had a tolerance for religion.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So during the classes, our home teacher would teach religion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the religion, all the Jewish kids were excused.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They could leave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never excused myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In fact, when my time came to say the prayer, I said the-- the Bulgarian prayer, recited it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But instead of crossing myself I had my-- my hands over my scrolls like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I never crossed myself, but he was so impressed with that, was our home teacher, that came to our home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He found out that my mother was a former teacher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He had a very great discussion here, and also asked her if I will be helpful to certain-- there were peasant children that were sent to high school there and they were having little difficult time, so I could help them in-- with their study.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that kind of-- of freedom we did enjoy in school, but were not allowed any Jewish activities.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In America, I was, but not in Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] No.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
